@startuml
left to right direction

' Style settings for clarity
skinparam actorStyle awesome
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam usecase {
    BackgroundColor #F3E5F5
    BorderColor #4A148C
    ArrowColor #4A148C
}
